      <abstract>
        <p>David Melancon will head new Denver office of Ogilvy Public Relations Worldwide as managing director (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>David Melancon was named to head a new Denver office of Ogilvy Public Relations Worldwide, part of the WPP Group, as managing director. He had been chief marketing officer at netLibrary, Boulder, Colo.</p>
